article.description: — Teddy Allen posted 16 points as New Mexico State got past UTEP 77-71 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Allen scores 16 to lead New Mexico State past UTEP 77-71
article.linkText: Allen scores 16 to lead New Mexico State past UTEP 77-71
article.story: LAS CRUCES, N.M. -- — Teddy Allen posted 16 points as New Mexico State got past UTEP 77-71 on Saturday night. Jabari Rice had 15 points for New Mexico State (2-0). Yuat Alok added 13 points. Donnie Tillman had 12 points. Souley Boum had 21 points for the Miners (1-1). Jamal Bieniemy added 13 points.
